I always appreciate uploads... but I must warn everyone.. DO NOT click on the link given here... It's just another spam site that requires you to register and sells your data.. and I think the uploaded makes money each time someone clicks on the link.  It's a shame users must be teases with a SINGLE comic with the promise of more... 

Well, in any case, thanks uploader for this upload, even though it's an old issue that's been uploaded a long time ago already.
Whoops... sorry for my typos and bad grammar in my previous message.. I didn't proof read before I sent it..  hahaha

no... you dont require to register and sell data... It's just a blog... check it out... 

It has got some awesome feedbacks... you can read it for yourself...
